>\n<br />\n唔係大陸傳入黎咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係, 外國傳先<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 手機 resolution : 無論係samsung, LG, HTC, 2560x1440 一樣叫2K<br />\n<br />\n大陸其實仲衰, 乜Q野超過2000 就叫2K...明明係隻21:9 1080p 都叫做2K</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係外國好似係叫開QHD或2.5K 凡有呢D Argument 外國人都好快分析到出黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://androidandme.com/thread/2560x1440-should-not-be-called-2k-its-far-better/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fandroidandme.com%2Fthread%2F2560x1440-should-not-be-called-2k-its-far-better%2F&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e4f88bcf\" target=\"_blank\">http://androidandme.com/thread/2560x1440-should-not-be-called-2k-its-far-better/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tomshardware.com/forum/id-2029839/1440p.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomshardware.com%2Fforum%2Fid-2029839%2F1440p.html&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=024e86e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tomshardware.com/forum/id-2029839/1440p.html</a><br />\n<br />\n懷疑係大陸D 2K手機傳入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfb5fa07c456dc78cf61ddd90fd876f0099c332","tid":134990,"uid":5335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:20:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed55fa33e29d700f72729b72feeae4c10f35bd7d","tid":134990,"uid":34165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔洗嘈啦<br />\n<br />\n🇭🇰冷🍚王 同 影男 冇講錯<br />\n<br />\n2K &quot;原本&quot;個definition 係 horizontal resolution around 2000<br />\n<br />\n&quot;原本&quot; 1440p 係叫返1440p / WQHD ... <br />\n<br />\n後尾D人叫叫下覺得要叫1440P太On9 , 咁啱又有4K mon既出現, 所以先叫1440p 做 2K <br />\n<br />\n其實姐係地鐵, 東鐵, 西鐵, 馬鐵, 輕鐵一樣咋嘛, 叫叫下全部變哂地鐵, 有咩好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係大陸傳入黎咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係, 外國傳先<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 手機 resolution : 無論係samsung, LG, HTC, 2560x1440 一樣叫2K<br />\n<br />\n大陸其實仲衰, 乜Q野超過2000 就叫2K...明明係隻21:9 1080p 都叫做2K</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係外國好似係叫開QHD或2.5K 凡有呢D Argument 外國人都好快分析到出黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://androidandme.com/thread/2560x1440-should-not-be-called-2k-its-far-better/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fandroidandme.com%2Fthread%2F2560x1440-should-not-be-called-2k-its-far-better%2F&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e4f88bcf\" target=\"_blank\">http://androidandme.com/thread/2560x1440-should-not-be-called-2k-its-far-better/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tomshardware.com/forum/id-2029839/1440p.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tomshardware.com%2Fforum%2Fid-2029839%2F1440p.html&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=024e86e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tomshardware.com/forum/id-2029839/1440p.html</a><br />\n<br />\n懷疑係大陸D 2K手機傳入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n.................................<br />\n會唔會斷章取義得太過份, 僅僅憑幾個人既留言就話其他人唔可以咁叫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newegg.com/4K-2K-Monitors/PromotionStore/ID-2032604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newegg.com%2F4K-2K-Monitors%2FPromotionStore%2FID-2032604&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e1583275\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newegg.com/4K-2K-Monitors/PromotionStore/ID-2032604</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/ASUS-MX27AQ-2560x1440-Frameless-Monitor/dp/B00VRKVGSC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FASUS-MX27AQ-2560x1440-Frameless-Monitor%2Fdp%2FB00VRKVGSC&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b507b91b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/ASUS-MX27AQ-2560x1440-Frameless-Monitor/dp/B00VRKVGSC</a><br />\n<br />\n以你既睇法, 係咪覺得newsgg 同amazon 個D全部錯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我直接Quote埋expertreviews 其中一句:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Sometimes QHD or WQHD is referred to as 2K, with the idea that it's half the 4K HD resolution found on high end TV sets (more about that later). But most of the time the 2K name cis derived from the larger of the pixel measurements being over 2,000 pixels. Technically, the resolution standard for 2K is 2,048&times;1,080, meaning QHD is actually much better in resolution. QHD could even be referred to as 2.5K, but some people resists in calling these displays 2K.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.expertreviews.co.uk/tvs-entertainment/1404464/whats-the-difference-between-wqhd-qhd-2k-4k-and-uhd-display-resolutions-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.expertreviews.co.uk%2Ftvs-entertainment%2F1404464%2Fwhats-the-difference-between-wqhd-qhd-2k-4k-and-uhd-display-resolutions-1&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ead798d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.expertreviews.co.uk/tvs-entertainment/1404464/whats-the-difference-between-wqhd-qhd-2k-4k-and-uhd-display-resolutions-1</a><br />\n<br />\n其實嘈黎好無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}